{"tid":48513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人係對節日冷感","createTime":"2016-12-21T06:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T11:29:42.000Z","uid":7805,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"535a8bc3f148227824b9726253d9379dd462ddce","tid":48513,"uid":7805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:15:27.000Z","msg":"我同我屋企人都對節日冷感<br />\n唔會特登迎合節日<br />\n連生日都唔會好在乎<br />\n有時有人俾驚喜自己先會醒起<br />\n以前細個會期待生日<br />\n依家覺得其實咩節日都係咁過<br />\n唔會特別開心或唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f09eb2178e0e5ada8bccdd9dbe81b8be8824f4","tid":48513,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:19:17.000Z","msg":"Same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831fc319c2354d507b776c7ec7a0fb3c78ddc4a5","tid":48513,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:24:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家只係想生日個日靜靜地過<br />\n唔想搞咩大龍鳳"},{"pid":"93ef6cab7ff03f85ebb36ba161adbd54fe77630f","tid":48513,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:35:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家只係想生日個日靜靜地過<br />\n唔想搞咩大龍鳳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想靜靜地過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b18446db80fe41df0db215a091093f91095324","tid":48513,"uid":22331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:37:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8704aa85f6c29c4fc34d3b1a92b244bdddb6409","tid":48513,"uid":16554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:37:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家只係想生日個日靜靜地過<br />\n唔想搞咩大龍鳳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"h